                  <h3 class="sub-heading">How We Share Personal Information</h3>
                  <p>Any information we collect through your use of our online services may be shared with our service providers, financial institutions with whom we jointly offer financial products, our affiliates, or as permitted or required by law (such as credit bureau agencies, business we buy or sell assets from, and law enforcement or government agencies).</p>
